{"tid":1473441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"討論如何運用外國勢力","createTime":"2019-08-15T00:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T00:58:41.000Z","uid":110403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e582491bf881cac7d99c2e713d4a405187b75c","tid":1473441,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:15:27.000Z","msg":"我地從來都冇話過比外國人聽點先幫到我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下開放討論 整返個類似五大訊求 比文宣組做野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拋磚引玉:<br />\n排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n罷買made in China <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d67c30119ab7ccb4e96e6bc765da60c79e1d61c","tid":1473441,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:15:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c66dbd252b9fd0aa1cea581e32f9422c2af7b1b","tid":1473441,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:15:49.000Z","msg":"外國勢力介入"},{"pid":"9eb53834cc956ca1468cf08d722fc746ad3bb4b8","tid":1473441,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"集思廣益"},{"pid":"2383a30a60eeffcc82f8963f9d4772d83c760fa3","tid":1473441,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:16:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd2b8182249d7582e52b00fb303779d6efbf1e1d","tid":1473441,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:17:24.000Z","msg":"比方向"},{"pid":"bf5744d763b4d6905ce55e8562989db40f37f2c0","tid":1473441,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:18:43.000Z","msg":"人呢"},{"pid":"0da523c5273f62ac8c39a629c742a5ff4883d10a","tid":1473441,"uid":110403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:24:48.000Z","msg":"推呀 成日叫人幫又冇實際行動"},{"pid":"d8d64fc3b9f81fc5a99d590bd9e3aa622cee5c17","tid":1473441,"uid":107052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:27:37.000Z","msg":"呼籲罷買made in China 我覺得冇問題，不過與其叫佢哋排華，不如我哋灌輸Hong kong is not China 嘅概念比佢哋？首先教育一下其實兩個地方係有分別先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多外國人唔識分香港人同中國人，更加唔知香港同中國有分別，所以如果直接叫佢哋歧視，其實會影響到自己人<br />\n<br />\n另外我哋可以收集外國 petition 整成QR code 做文宣 ，再用 #standwithhk / 其他hashtag 呼籲佢哋都可以上網同朋友講幫手簽 petition<br />\n<br />\n如果遇上更有心嘅外國人，可以呼籲佢哋去信自己國家嘅議員關注香港議題，用佢哋本地公民個身份施壓 （特別係英國班MP）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883a3b868bee1003977438c84c4c07144d479c0f","tid":1473441,"uid":12130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:27:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=b590c18d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=b590c18d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"1e73ab8212b88699368a1a5c20d80ede0adda2b3","tid":1473441,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"唔止美國 其他國家 英澳加等國 一齊攪香港人權與民主法案 要所有賣港官員其他地方都去唔到 共享大灣區榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}